reviews.review_text: And Leave it On!!!!! Long, sweet, rocking show.... had it all..... First set was loooonnnggg!!!!  Second set was hot!!!  Great NFA> Lovelight..... Remember strolling the streets of Hartford after the show and hearing all the folks singing Lovelight.....  Lived in CT from 83 to 99 and saw some great shows in Hartford [sound was always interesting in the Civic Center].... This is one of my favorites....

Still on... So glad to find this show.  I, too, remember pouring out into the Hartford night singing "Lovelight."  So lost in the post-show glow and eager to get to the iced-down beer ball in my car, I was almost run down by Lesh's limo exiting the venue.  He smirked, we cheered and all was right.  This was one of many great early 80s shows at this venue.

Great FOB recording!
